| Type                  | Syntax Example             | Description                               |
| --------------------- | -------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| Positional            | `func("Alice", 25)`        | Order matters                             |
| Default               | `def func(name="User")`    | Uses default if argument not provided     |
| Keyword               | `func(name="Bob", age=30)` | Explicitly specifies parameters           |
| Variable (\*args)     | `def func(*args)`          | Accepts many positional values as tuple   |
| Variable (\*\*kwargs) | `def func(**kwargs)`       | Accepts many keyword values as dictionary |
